title: Bobby Gets A Message From Keith Urban After Winning ACM Award + Hospital Update From Lunchbox + Country Artist Travis Denning Co-Hosts
itunes:title: Bobby Gets A Message From Keith Urban After Winning ACM Award + Hospital Update From Lunchbox + Country Artist Travis Denning Co-Hosts
description:
We won a big award yesterday and Keith Urban sent Bobby a cool message to congratulate the show. Eddie went to the hospital to get an update from Lunchbox after welcoming their second child! Plus, country artist Travis Denning stops by to fill-in for Lunchbox!
